  MODULE .......: mandarina_icc_checker.p
  TASK .........: Program removes Mandarina redirection if it is active
                  when ICC is done.
  APPLICATION ..: tms
  AUTHOR .......: ilsavola
  CREATED ......: 08/2017
  Version ......: yoigo
----------------------------------------------------------------------
10/01/2018 ashok YDR-2754 Inactivate Barring after ICC Change
                          Code optimization
---------------------------------------------------------------------- */

